de.parsemis.graph
Class ListGraph<NodeType,EdgeType>

java.lang.Object
  de.parsemis.graph.ListGraph<NodeType,EdgeType>
Type Parameters:
NodeType - the type of the node labels (will be hashed and checked with .equals(..))
EdgeType - the type of the edge labels (will be hashed and checked with .equals(..))
All Implemented Interfaces:
Graph<NodeType,EdgeType>, MutableGraph<NodeType,EdgeType>, Cloneable<Graph<NodeType,EdgeType>>, Generic<NodeType,EdgeType>, java.io.Serializable
public class ListGraph<NodeType,EdgeType>
extends java.lang.Object
implements MutableGraph<NodeType,EdgeType>

List-based implementation of the MutableGraph interface.

It stores the required node and edge informations in different lists (ArrayList and arrays).

Author:
Marc Woerlein (woerlein@informatik.uni-erlangen.de)
